{"tid":2052040,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連登女神周麗淇香港剖腹誕金牛B 囝囝似足大陸演員爸爸傅浤鳴","createTime":"2020-06-05T08:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T06:25:57.000Z","uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8eabc82681eeab72f56eb9c308d843d5c6637550","tid":2052040,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:14:50.000Z","msg":"現年40歲嘅周麗淇（Niki）前年下嫁內地男演員傅浤鳴，翌年就宣布有喜，據知Niki半個月前已經順利誕下Ｂ仔喇！消息指Niki於5月18日喺舊山頂嘉諾撒醫院剖腹誕下6磅重囝囝，BB鼻高高個樣似足爸爸。Niki依家正於家中坐月，並餵哺母乳，除咗有請陪月員悉心照顧外，仲有老公幫忙湊仔，一切安好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2660000/2661318/unname_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2660000%2F2661318%2Funname_1024.jpg&h=db924d77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n錫到Niki燶嘅傅浤鳴本來忙於在內地拍劇，但為陪伴太太同迎接二人嘅首個愛情結晶品，所以一早已經到港陪老婆，貼身照顧做跟得老公。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2660000/2661318/0082feGMly1gcqgvrskrsj30u01hc4qp_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2660000%2F2661318%2F0082feGMly1gcqgvrskrsj30u01hc4qp_600.jpg&h=a9a1ba5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傅浤鳴喺大陸係人氣演員。（微博圖片）<br />\n<br />\n而Niki一知道懷孕後已盡量少外出及減少與朋友見面，連主演嘅電影後期宣傳活動都冇去，淨係出席過朋友嘅生日會同Baby Shower，其他時間都留在家中，閒時就玩吓煮飯仔。一向身形高挑瘦削嘅Niki產後豐滿咗少少，全因佢佗B期間有Keep住做適量運動，同名模家姐周汶錡一樣得天獨厚，係個靚媽。據知育有兩位得意囝囝嘅周汶錡都有經常去妹妹家中探望BB，照顧妹妹身體之餘，又傳授育兒心得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2660000/2661318/67631287_159690338424434_2875745878365279690_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2660000%2F2661318%2F67631287_159690338424434_2875745878365279690_n_600.jpg&h=60a7634d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNiki同家姐姊妹情深。（周汶錡IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2660000/2661318/30916517_243505286209859_7433394581741240320_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2660000%2F2661318%2F30916517_243505286209859_7433394581741240320_n_600.jpg&h=f3963922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周汶錡兩個混血B仔又多個小表弟做玩伴喇～（周勵淇IG）<br />\n<br />\n撰文：黃蘊姿"},{"pid":"9cf75b18abe925a9303ac63d782814755172a909","tid":2052040,"uid":203799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:16:00.000Z","msg":"邊到似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd6df3240b58a5f67cded5a022fa4c874a52214","tid":2052040,"uid":283741,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"點解啲明星咁鍾意剖腹？係咪驚人睇蝕個閪？"},{"pid":"d9d086f4eb7ba058688b87cfa838690026ac811d","tid":2052040,"uid":33999,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"dfd6df3240b58a5f67cded5a022fa4c874a52214","tid":2052040,"uid":283741,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"點解啲明星咁鍾意剖腹？係咪驚人睇蝕個閪？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"無咁痛<br />\n唔駛等<br />\n勸你問之前check 下IQ 先"},{"pid":"ae7cc990ed84780110cb4f27cd2d9813a86e87d7","tid":2052040,"uid":45170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9d086f4eb7ba058688b87cfa838690026ac811d","tid":2052040,"uid":33999,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"dfd6df3240b58a5f67cded5a022fa4c874a52214","tid":2052040,"uid":283741,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"點解啲明星咁鍾意剖腹？係咪驚人睇蝕個閪？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"無咁痛<br />\n唔駛等<br />\n勸你問之前check 下IQ 先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07955a1358ad40ad978c63e497216e7232a007d5","tid":2052040,"uid":355064,"like":